title: NFL Week 16: Brian Billick & Dark Horse MVP Candidates
itunes:title: NFL Week 16: Brian Billick & Dark Horse MVP Candidates
description:
Cynthia Frelund and Matt "Money" Smith break down the NFL's MVP race in the final weeks of the season and preview every Week 16 game. Former NFL Head Coach Brian Billick also joins the show, sitting down with Cynthia to discuss how the Pittsburgh Steelers can recover from their injuries to be successful in the playoffs.
